Create PDF books from RSS

You need to grab Prince from this page: http://www.princexml.com/download/ and have it installed on the same machine as the Bookler code. Please note a license is required for any commerical/professional use of Prince.

Start via ruby -rubygems booker.rb

Once the feed has been run, save the source html to index.html then run

prince -s public/stylesheets/kindle.css index.html -o index.pdf

Right now the CSS is configured for Kindle